&lt;p&gt;The tool will then walk you through a series of questions, asking you for your package name, version, and other details. In a few moments, your new package will be ready to go! It’s that simple.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Why-I-Built-This&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Why-I-Built-This&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Why I Built This&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Why I Built This&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I built &lt;code&gt;build-a-npm&lt;/code&gt; out of a personal need. I wanted a tool that would allow me to quickly scaffold new projects without getting bogged down in boilerplate. My goal was to create something that was not only powerful but also intuitive and fun to use. It’s an open-source tool, and I’m really excited to see what amazing things people build with it.&lt;/p&gt;
